  (8987, 11, 7, 45, 'And the pots, and the shovels, and the basins: and all these vessels, which Hiram made to king Solomon for the house of the LORD, were of bright brass.', '2~05518~, 5~03257~, 8~04219~: 12~03627~, 14~02438~ 15~06213~ 17~04428~ 18~08010~ 21~01004~ 24~03068~, [25 26] 27~04178~ 28~05178~.'),
