  (19091, 24, 5, 24, 'Neither say they in their heart, Let us now fear the LORD our God, that giveth rain, both the former and the latter, in his season: he reserveth unto us the appointed weeks of the harvest.', '1~0559~ 5~03824~, 9~03372~ 11~03068~ 13~0430~, 15~05414~ 16~01653~, 19~03138~ 22~04456~, 25~06256~: 27~08104~ 31~02708~ 32~07620~ 35~07105~.'),
