  (13135, 18, 11, 18, 'And thou shalt be secure, because there is hope; yea, thou shalt dig about thee, and thou shalt take thy rest in safety.', '4~0982~, 7~03426~ 8~08615~; 12~02658~ [13 15] 20~07901~ 22~0983~.'),
