  (17354, 21, 2, 12, 'And I turned myself to behold wisdom, and madness, and folly: for what can the man do that cometh after the king? even that which hath been already done.', '&para; 2~06437~ 5~07200~ 6~02451~, 8~01947~, 10~05531~: [13] 15~0120~ [16] 18~0935~ 19~0310~ 21~04428~? [22] 27~03528~ 28~06213~.'),
