  (1316, 1, 43, 21, 'And it came to pass, when we came to the inn, that we opened our sacks, and, behold, every man''s money was in the mouth of his sack, our money in full weight: and we have brought it again in our hand.', '7~0935~ 10~04411~, 13~06605~ 15~0572~, [18] 19~0376~ 20~03701~ [21] 24~06310~ 27~0572~, 29~03701~ 32~04948~: 38~07725~ 41~03027~.'),
  (7910, 9, 25, 42, 'And Abigail hasted, and arose, and rode upon an ass, with five damsels of hers that went after her; and she went after the messengers of David, and became his wife.', '1~026~ 2~04116~, 4~06965~, 6~07392~ 9~02543~, 11~02568~ 12~05291~ 16~01980~ 17~07272~ 21~03212~ 22~0310~ 24~04397~ 26~01732~, 30~0802~.'),
  (9905, 12, 14, 1, 'In the second year of Joash son of Jehoahaz king of Israel reigned Amaziah the son of Joash king of Judah.', '&para; 2~08147~ 3~08141~ 5~03101~ 6~01121~ 8~03099~ 9~04428~ 11~03478~ 12~04427~ 13~0558~ 15~01121~ 17~03101~ 18~04428~ 20~03063~.'),
