  (14624, 19, 46, 1, 'To the chief Musician for the sons of Korah, A Song upon Alamoth. God is our refuge and strength, a very present help in trouble.', '&para; [0 3~05329~ 6~01121~ 8~07141~, 10~07892~ 12] 12~05961~ 13~0430~ [14] 16~04268~ 18~05797~, 20~03966~ 21~04672~ 22~05833~ 24~06869~.'),
  (16099, 19, 122, 1, 'A Song of degrees of David. I was glad when they said unto me, Let us go into the house of the LORD.', '&para; [0 1~07892~ 3~04609~ 5] 5~01732~ 8~08055~ 11~0559~ 16~03212~ 19~01004~ 22~03068~.'),
  (7431, 9, 10, 6, 'And the spirit of the LORD will come upon thee, and thou shalt prophesy with them, and shalt be turned into another man.', '2~07307~ 5~03068~ 7~06743~ 13~05012~ 19~02015~ 21~0312~ 22~0376~.'),
  (1558, 2, 1, 21, 'And it came to pass, because the midwives feared God, that he made them houses.', '7~03205~ 8~03372~ 9~0430~, 12~06213~ 14~01004~.'),
  (28906, 47, 5, 13, 'For whether we be beside ourselves, it is to God: or whether we be sober, it is for your cause.', '0~1063~ 1~1535~ 5~1839~, [6 7] 9~2316~: 11~1535~ 14~4993~, [15 16] 19~5213~.'),
  (7895, 9, 25, 27, 'And now this blessing which thine handmaid hath brought unto my lord, let it even be given unto the young men that follow my lord.', '3~01293~ 6~08198~ 8~0935~ 11~0113~, 16~05414~ 20~05288~ 22~01980~ 23~07272~* 25~0113~.'),
  (24611, 41, 10, 12, 'And if a woman shall put away her husband, and be married to another, she committeth adultery.', '0~2532~ 1~1437~ 3~1135~ 6~630~ 7~846~ 8~435~, 9~2532~ 11~1060~ 13~243~, 16~3429~.'),
  (15448, 19, 94, 8, 'Understand, ye brutish among the people: and ye fools, when will ye be wise?', '0~0995~, 2~01197~ 5~05971~: [7] 8~03684~, 13~07919~?'),
  (5479, 5, 22, 3, 'In like manner shalt thou do with his ass; and so shalt thou do with his raiment; and with all lost thing of thy brother''s, which he hath lost, and thou hast found, shalt thou do likewise: thou mayest not hide thyself.', '2~03651~ 5~06213~ 8~02543~; 13~06213~ 16~08071~; 21~09~ 24~0251~, 28~06~, 32~04672~, 35~06213~ 38~03201~ 40~05956~'),
  (14969, 19, 69, 25, 'Let their habitation be desolate; and let none dwell in their tents.', '2~02918~ 4~08074~; [5] 8~03427~ 11~0168~.'),
  (2591, 2, 36, 20, 'And he made boards for the tabernacle of shittim wood, standing up.', '2~06213~ 3~07175~ 6~04908~ [7] 8~07848~ 9~06086~, 11~05975~.'),
  (4650, 4, 29, 36, 'But ye shall offer a burnt offering, a sacrifice made by fire, of a sweet savour unto the LORD: one bullock, one ram, seven lambs of the first year without blemish:', '3~07126~ 6~05930~, 11~0801~, 14~05207~ 15~07381~ 18~03068~: 19~0259~ 20~06499~, 21~0259~ 22~0352~, 23~07651~ 24~03532~ 27~01121~ 28~08141~ 30~08549~:'),
  (10054, 12, 18, 22, 'But if ye say unto me, We trust in the LORD our God: is not that he, whose high places and whose altars Hezekiah hath taken away, and hath said to Judah and Jerusalem, Ye shall worship before this altar in Jerusalem?', '3~0559~ 7~0982~ 10~03068~ 12~0430~: [13] 19~01116~ 22~04196~ 23~02396~ 26~05493~, 29~0559~ 31~03063~ 33~03389~, 36~07812~ 37~06440~ 39~04196~ 41~03389~?'),
  (27307, 44, 10, 32, 'Send therefore to Joppa, and call hither Simon, whose surname is Peter; he is lodged in the house of one Simon a tanner by the sea side: who, when he cometh, shall speak unto thee.', '0~3992~ 1~3767~ 2~1519~ 3~2445~, 4~2532~ 6~3333~ 7~4613~, 8~3739~ 10~1941~ 11~4074~; 12~3778~ 14~3579~ 15~1722~ 17~3614~ [19] 20~4613~ 22~1038~ 23~3844~ 26~2281~: 27~3739~, 30~3854~, 32~2980~ 34~4671~.'),
  (839, 1, 30, 5, 'And Bilhah conceived, and bare Jacob a son.', '1~01090~ 2~02029~, 4~03205~ 5~03290~ 7~01121~.'),
  (6389, 6, 21, 1, 'Then came near the heads of the fathers of the Levites unto Eleazar the priest, and unto Joshua the son of Nun, and unto the heads of the fathers of the tribes of the children of Israel;', '&para; 2~05066~ 4~07218~ 7~01~ 10~03881~ 12~0499~ 14~03548~, 17~03091~ 19~01121~ 21~05126~, 25~07218~ 28~01~ 31~04294~ 34~01121~ 36~03478~;'),
  (27481, 44, 15, 23, 'And they wrote letters by them after this manner; The apostles and elders and brethren send greeting unto the brethren which are of the Gentiles in Antioch and Syria and Cilicia:', '2~1125~ [3] 4~1223~ 5~846~ 6~5495~ 8~3592~; 10~652~ 11~2532~ 12~4245~ 13~2532~ 14~80~ [15] 16~5463~ 19~80~ 20~3588~ 22~1537~ 24~1484~ 25~2596~ 26~490~ 27~2532~ 28~4947~ 29~2532~ 30~2791~:'),
  (30455, 60, 3, 15, 'But sanctify the Lord God in your hearts: and be ready always to give an answer to every man that asketh you a reason of the hope that is in you with meekness and fear:', '0~1161~ 1~37~ 3~2962~ 4~2316~ 5~1722~ 6~5216~ 7~2588~: 8~1161~ [9] 10~2092~ 11~104~ 12~4314~ [13] 15~627~ 18~3956~ 20~154~ 21~5209~ 23~3056~ 24~4012~ 26~1680~ 29~1722~ 30~5213~ 31~3326~ 32~4240~ 33~2532~ 34~5401~:'),
