  (25034, 42, 2, 49, 'And he said unto them, How is it that ye sought me? wist ye not that I must be about my Father''s business?', '0~2532~ 2~2036~ 3~4314~ 4~846~, 5~5101~ 8~3754~ 10~2212~ 11~3165~? 13~1492~ 14~3756~ 15~3754~ 16~3165~ 17~1163~ 18~1511~ 19~1722~ 20~3450~ 22~3962~?'),
