  (11995, 14, 35, 20, 'After all this, when Josiah had prepared the temple, Necho king of Egypt came up to fight against Charchemish by Euphrates: and Josiah went out against him.', '&para; 0~0310~ 4~02977~ 6~03559~ 8~01004~, 9~05224~ 10~04428~ 12~04714~ 14~05927~ 16~03898~ 18~03751~ 20~06578~: 22~02977~ 24~03318~ 25~07125~'),
  (62, 1, 3, 6, 'And when the woman saw that the tree was good for food, and that it was pleasant to the eyes, and a tree to be desired to make one wise, she took of the fruit thereof, and did eat, and gave also unto her husband with her; and he did eat.', '&para; 3~0802~ 4~07200~ 7~06086~ [8] 9~02896~ 11~03978~, 14~01931~ [15] 16~08378~ 19~05869~, 22~06086~ 25~02530~ [28] 29~07919~, 31~03947~ 35~06529~, 38~0398~, 40~05414~ 41~01571~ 44~0376~ 50~0398~.'),
  (26181, 43, 4, 10, 'Jesus answered and said unto her, If thou knewest the gift of God, and who it is that saith to thee, Give me to drink; thou wouldest have asked of him, and he would have given thee living water.', '0~2424~ 1~611~ 2~2532~ 3~2036~ 5~846~, 6~1487~ 8~1492~ 10~1431~ 12~2316~, 13~2532~ 14~5101~ 16~2076~ 18~3004~ 20~4671~, 21~1325~ 22~3427~ 24~4095~; 25~4771~ 26~302~ 28~154~ 30~846~, 31~2532~ 33~302~ 35~1325~ 36~4671~ 37~2198~ 38~5204~.'),
  (8046, 10, 1, 17, 'And David lamented with this lamentation over Saul and over Jonathan his son:', '&para; 1~01732~ 2~06969~ 5~07015~ 7~07586~ 10~03083~ 12~01121~:'),
  (9408, 11, 19, 13, 'And it was so, when Elijah heard it that he wrapped his face in his mantle, and went out, and stood in the entering in of the cave. And, behold, there came a voice unto him, and said, What doest thou here, Elijah?', '[3] 5~0452~ 6~08085~ [7] 10~03874~ 12~06440~ 15~0155~, 18~03318~, 20~05975~ 24~06607~ 27~04631~. [30 31] 33~06963~ 37~0559~, 42~0452~?'),
  (7574, 9, 15, 7, 'And Saul smote the Amalekites from Havilah until thou comest to Shur, that is over against Egypt.', '1~07586~ 2~05221~ 4~06002~ 6~02341~ [7] 9~0935~ 11~07793~, [13] 15~06440~ 16~04714~.'),
  (17902, 23, 11, 9, 'They shall not hurt nor destroy in all my holy mountain: for the earth shall be full of the knowledge of the LORD, as the waters cover the sea.', '3~07489~ 5~07843~ 9~06944~ 10~02022~: 13~0776~ 16~04390~ 19~01844~ 22~03068~, 25~04325~ 26~03680~ 28~03220~.'),
  (30980, 66, 16, 10, 'And the fifth angel poured out his vial upon the seat of the beast; and his kingdom was full of darkness; and they gnawed their tongues for pain,', '0~2532~ 2~3991~ 3~32~ 5~1632~ 6~846~ 7~5357~ 8~1909~ 10~2362~ 13~2342~; 14~2532~ 15~846~ 16~932~ 17~1096~ 20~4656~; 21~2532~ 23~3145~ 24~846~ 25~1100~ 26~1537~ 27~4192~,'),
  (29535, 51, 3, 2, 'Set your affection on things above, not on things on the earth.', '2~5426~ 5~507~, 6~3361~ 9~1909~ 11~1093~.'),
  (9951, 12, 15, 18, 'And he did that which was evil in the sight of the LORD: he departed not all his days from the sins of Jeroboam the son of Nebat, who made Israel to sin.', '2~06213~ [3 5] 6~07451~ 9~05869~ 12~03068~: 14~05493~ 18~03117~ 21~02403~ 23~03379~ 25~01121~ 27~05028~, 30~03478~ 32~02398~.'),
  (10554, 13, 7, 11, 'All these the sons of Jediael, by the heads of their fathers, mighty men of valour, were seventeen thousand and two hundred soldiers, fit to go out for war and battle.', '3~01121~ 5~03043~, 8~07218~ 11~01~, 12~01368~ 15~02428~, [16] 17~06240~ 18~07651~* 19~0505~ 22~03967~ [23] 27~03318~ 29~06635~ [30] 31~04421~.'),
  (4883, 4, 35, 32, 'And ye shall take no satisfaction for him that is fled to the city of his refuge, that he should come again to dwell in the land, until the death of the priest.', '3~03947~ 5~03724~ 10~05127~ 13~05892~ 16~04733~, 21~07725~ 23~03427~ 26~0776~, 29~04194~ 32~03548~.'),
  (16111, 19, 123, 4, 'Our soul is exceedingly filled with the scorning of those that are at ease, and with the contempt of the proud.', '1~05315~ 3~07227~ 4~07646~ 7~03933~ 13~07600~, [14] 17~0937~ 20~03238~'),
  (24761, 41, 13, 33, 'Take ye heed, watch and pray: for ye know not when the time is.', '2~991~, 3~69~ 4~2532~ 5~4336~: 6~1063~ 8~1492~ 9~3756~ 10~4219~ 12~2540~ 13~2076~.'),
  (7197, 8, 3, 18, 'Then said she, Sit still, my daughter, until thou know how the matter will fall: for the man will not be in rest, until he have finished the thing this day.', '1~0559~ 4~03427~, 6~01323~, 9~03045~ 12~01697~ 14~05307~: 17~0376~ 22~08252~, 23~0518~ 26~03615~ 28~01697~ 30~03117~.'),
  (1242, 1, 41, 42, 'And Pharaoh took off his ring from his hand, and put it upon Joseph''s hand, and arrayed him in vestures of fine linen, and put a gold chain about his neck;', '1~06547~ 3~05493~ 5~02885~ 8~03027~, 10~05414~ 13~03130~ 14~03027~, 16~03847~ 19~0899~ 22~08336~, 24~07760~ 26~02091~ 27~07242~ 30~06677~;'),
  (30405, 60, 1, 15, 'But as he which hath called you is holy, so be ye holy in all manner of conversation;', '0~235~ 1~2596~ 5~2564~ 6~5209~ 8~40~, 9~2532~ 10~1096~ 11~846~ 12~40~ 13~1722~ 14~3956~ 17~391~;'),
  (18804, 23, 58, 9, 'Then shalt thou call, and the LORD shall answer; thou shalt cry, and he shall say, Here I am. If thou take away from the midst of thee the yoke, the putting forth of the finger, and speaking vanity;', '3~07121~, 6~03068~ 8~06030~; 11~07768~, 15~0559~, [18] 22~05493~ 25~08432~ 29~04133~, 32~07971~ 35~0676~, 37~01696~ 38~0205~;'),
  (26106, 43, 1, 47, 'Jesus saw Nathanael coming to him, and saith of him, Behold an Israelite indeed, in whom is no guile!', '0~2424~ 1~1492~ 2~3482~ 3~2064~ 4~4314~ 5~846~, 6~2532~ 7~3004~ 8~4012~ 9~846~, 10~2396~ 12~2475~ 13~230~, 14~1722~ 15~3739~ 16~2076~ 17~3756~ 18~1388~!'),
  (16034, 19, 119, 127, 'Therefore I love thy commandments above gold; yea, above fine gold.', '&para; 2~0157~ 4~04687~ 6~02091~; 10~06337~.'),
