  (19486, 24, 22, 23, 'O inhabitant of Lebanon, that makest thy nest in the cedars, how gracious shalt thou be when pangs come upon thee, the pain as of a woman in travail!', '1~03427~ 3~03844~, 7~07077~ 10~0730~, 12~02603~ 17~02256~ 18~0935~ 22~02427~ 28~03205~!'),
