  (3246, 3, 17, 6, 'And the priest shall sprinkle the blood upon the altar of the LORD at the door of the tabernacle of the congregation, and burn the fat for a sweet savour unto the LORD.', '2~03548~ 4~02236~ 6~01818~ 9~04196~ 12~03068~ [13] 15~06607~ 18~0168~ 21~04150~, 23~06999~ 25~02459~ 28~05207~ 29~07381~ 32~03068~.'),
