  (18766, 23, 56, 4, 'For thus saith the LORD unto the eunuchs that keep my sabbaths, and choose the things that please me, and take hold of my covenant;', '2~0559~ 4~03068~ 7~05631~ 9~08104~ 11~07676~, 13~0977~ [14 15] 17~02654~ 21~02388~ 24~01285~;'),
