  (24851, 41, 15, 14, 'Then Pilate said unto them, Why, what evil hath he done? And they cried out the more exceedingly, Crucify him.', '0~1161~ 1~4091~ 2~3004~ 4~846~, 5~1063~, 6~5101~ 7~2556~ 10~4160~? 11~1161~ 14~2896~ 17~4056~, 18~4717~ 19~846~.'),
