  (5257, 5, 12, 11, 'Then there shall be a place which the LORD your God shall choose to cause his name to dwell there; thither shall ye bring all that I command you; your burnt offerings, and your sacrifices, your tithes, and the heave offering of your hand, and all your choice vows which ye vow unto the LORD:', '5~04725~ 8~03068~ 10~0430~ 12~0977~ 16~08034~ 18~07931~ 23~0935~ 27~06680~ 31~05930~, 34~02077~, 36~04643~, 40~08641~ 43~03027~, 47~04005~ 48~05088~ 51~05087~ 54~03068~:'),
