  (1236, 1, 41, 36, 'And that food shall be for store to the land against the seven years of famine, which shall be in the land of Egypt; that the land perish not through the famine.', '2~0400~ 6~06487~ 9~0776~ 12~07651~ 13~08141~ 15~07458~, 21~0776~ 23~04714~; 26~0776~ 27~03772~ 31~07458~.'),
