  (26250, 43, 5, 25, 'Verily, verily, I say unto you, The hour is coming, and now is, when the dead shall hear the voice of the Son of God: and they that hear shall live.', '0~281~, 1~281~, 3~3004~ 5~5213~ 6~3754~,* 8~5610~ 10~2064~, 11~2532~ 12~3568~ 13~2076~, 14~3753~ 16~3498~ 18~191~ 20~5456~ 23~5207~ 25~2316~: 26~2532~ 29~191~ 31~2198~.'),
