  (21259, 26, 32, 2, 'Son of man, take up a lamentation for Pharaoh king of Egypt, and say unto him, Thou art like a young lion of the nations, and thou art as a whale in the seas: and thou camest forth with thy rivers, and troubledst the waters with thy feet, and fouledst their rivers.', '0~01121~ 2~0120~, 4~05375~ 6~07015~ 8~06547~ 9~04428~ 11~04714~, 13~0559~ 18~01819~ 21~03715~ 24~01471~, [27] 30~08577~ 31~08565~* 34~03220~: 38~01518~ 41~05104~, 43~01804~ 45~04325~ 48~07272~, 50~07515~ 52~05104~.'),
