  (23669, 40, 15, 26, 'But he answered and said, It is not meet to take the children''s bread, and cast it to dogs.', '0~1161~ 2~611~ 4~2036~, 6~2076~ 7~3756~ 8~2570~ 10~2983~ 12~5043~ 13~740~, 14~2532~ 16~906~ [17] 19~2952~.'),
