  (20091, 24, 48, 2, 'There shall be no more praise of Moab: in Heshbon they have devised evil against it; come, and let us cut it off from being a nation. Also thou shalt be cut down, O Madmen; the sword shall pursue thee.', '[0 2] 5~08416~ 7~04124~: 9~02809~ 12~02803~ 13~07451~ 16~03212~, 22~03772~ [24] 26~01471~. 32~01826~, 34~04086~; 36~02719~ 38~03212~ 39~0310~.'),
